| No tasks to unlink |\r\n85. \r\n86. #### MCP Tools to Retain (unchanged, ~15 tools)\r\n87. \r\n88. | Tool | Module | Purpose |\r\n89. |------|--------|---------|\r\n90. | `set_workspace` | lifecycle.rs | Bind to workspace, trigger hydration |\r\n91. | `get_daemon_status` | lifecycle.rs | Report uptime, connections |\r\n92. | `get_workspace_status` | lifecycle.rs | Report code graph and content stats (modified) |\r\n93. | `index_workspace` | write.rs | Full AST parse + embedding |\r\n94. | `sync_workspace` | write.rs | Incremental index of modified files |\r\n95. | `map_code` | read.rs | List code nodes with filters |\r\n96. | `list_symbols` | read.rs | Search symbols by name/type/language |\r\n97. | `query_graph` | read.rs | Custom graph traversal (callers, callees, imports) |\r\n98. | `impact_analysis` | read.rs | Code-only impact of changes (modified) |\r\n99. | `unified_search` | read.rs | Vector + lexical search across code and content (modified) |\r\n100. | `get_health_report` | read.rs | Code graph health (modified) |\r\n101. | `flush_state` | write.rs | Serialize code graph to `.engram/` (modified) |\r\n102. | `index_git_history` | write.rs | Git commit ingestion (feature-gated) |\r\n103. | `query_changes` | read.rs | Git change tracing (feature-gated) |\r\n104. \r\n105. #### Models to Remove\r\n106. \r\n107. | File | Structs |\r\n108. |------|---------|\r\n109. | `src/models/task.rs` | `Task`, `TaskStatus`, `TaskRow` |\r\n110. | `src/models/graph.rs` | `DependencyType` (task dependency edges) |\r\n111. | `src/models/context.rs` | `Context`, `ContextRow` (task audit notes) |\r\n112. | `src/models/label.rs` | `Label`, `LabelRow` |\r\n113. | `src/models/comment.rs` | `Comment`, `CommentRow` |\r\n114. | `src/models/event.rs` | `Event`, `EventKind`, `EventRow` |\r\n115. | `src/models/spec.rs` | `Spec`, `SpecRow` |\r\n116. | `src/models/collection.rs` | `Collection`, `CollectionRow` |\r\n117. | `src/models/backlog.rs` | `BacklogFile`, `ProjectManifest` |\r\n118.